Thanks for your contribution. Looks good, but I have a few small comments.

```suggestion
/-- The symmetric difference of two `iSup`s is at most
```
This should probably be `le_symmDiff_sup_right` (or `left_le_symmDiff_sup`). Can you also add a version with `y ∆ x` instead of `x ∆ y`?

```suggestion
  convert symmDiff_triangle x y ⊥ <;> rw [symmDiff_bot]
```
if you want, this is a shortened proof. But feel free to leave it as-is.
Thanks for this! I did not know about `convert`.
